high_descs: Turn right and head to the round black table.
Pick up the mug on the right.
Turn around and bring the mug to the microwave.
Heat the mug in the microwave.
Bring the heated mug to the coffee machine on the left.
Put the mug on the coffee machine.
anns.task_desc: Put a heated mug on the coffee machine.

high_descs: Turn right and walk across the room to the round dining table
Pick up the white mug left of the cup from the table
Turn around and walk across the kitchen to the microwave
Heat the mug in the microwave then remove it
Turn left and walk up to the coffee maker on the counter
Put the mug in the coffee maker
anns.task_desc: Put the heated mug in the coffee maker

high_descs: Turn around, go straight, and then turn left to approach the round table.
Pick up the mug on the table, in front of the salt.
Turn around and go to the microwave on the counter.
Heat the mug in the microwave.
Turn left to face the dishwasher.
Put the mug at the coffee maker, above the dishwasher.
anns.task_desc: Put a warm mug at the coffee maker.

high_descs: Turn around and then go left to the round black table.
Pick up the white mug front the round table.
Take the mug, turn around and go straight back to the microwave.
Put the mug in the microwave and turn it on. When finished, remove the mug from the microwave.
Take the mug a few steps to the left to the coffee maker.
Put the mug on the coffee maker.
anns.task_desc: Heat up a mug and make some coffee.

high_descs: Turn around and head left until you reach the kitchen table
Pick up a mug from off of the table
Turn around and walk to the microwave
Open the microwave door and heat the mug in the microwave for a few seconds, before taking it out
Turn left to face the coffee maker
Place the mug on the coffee maker
anns.task_desc: Place a heated mug on a coffee maker
